task.en: Help me extract the text from a research paper. You can find the paper at Documents/benchmark_files/PDF/1312.6199v4.pdf. Save the extracted text as a txt file with the same file name on Desktop.

pre_command: osascript -e 'tell application "Automator" to activate' && osascript -e 'tell application "Finder" to close windows' && rm -rf /Users/ec2-user/Documents/benchmark_files/ && cp -r /Users/ec2-user/Benchmark_Backup/benchmark_files /Users/ec2-user/Documents && open /Users/ec2-user/Documents/benchmark_files/PDF
